<p source="SHANGBO.MING 8.47.1 (STRIPS 1,2) MACHENGYUAN 8: 192, 193 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.1">葉公子高之子見於令尹子春，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.2">子春謂之曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.3">“君王窮亡人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.4">命吾爲楚邦.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.5">恐不【1】能，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.6">以辱斧鑕.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.7">先大夫之諷誡命，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-1a.8">亦可以告我”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MING 8.47.2 (STRIPS 2-3, 6) MACHENGYUAN 8: 193-194, 197 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.1">答曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.2">“僕既得辱視日 【2】之廷，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.3">命求言以答，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.4">雖剥[=裂]於斧鑕，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.5">命勿之敢違.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.6">如以僕之觀視日也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-2a.7">【3】十又三亡僕.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MING 8.47.3 (STRIPS 6-7) MACHENGYUAN 8: 197-198 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.1">令尹曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.2">“先大夫嗣令尹,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.3">受司馬，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.4">治楚邦之政，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.5">黔首萬民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.6">【6】莫不欣喜；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.7">四海之內，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.8">莫弗聞[信].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.9">子謂陽爲賢於先大夫，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-3a.10">請問其故.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MING 8.47.4 (STRIPS 7-9) MACHENGYUAN 8: 198-200 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.1">答曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.2">【7】“亡僕之掌楚邦之政，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.3">坐友五人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.4">立友七人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.5">君王之所以命</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.6">與所爲於楚【8】邦，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.7">必內偶 *ŋooʔ [叩 *khooʔ]  之於十又三，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.8">皆亡留[謬]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-4a.9">而行之.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MING 8.47.5 (STRIPS 9-10) MACHENGYUAN 8: 200-201 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a.1">今視日爲楚令尹，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a.2">坐友亡【9】一人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a.3">立友亡一人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a.4">而邦政不敗，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a.5">僕以此謂</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-5a.6">視日十又三亡僕.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.MING 8.47.6 (STRIPS10-11A) MACHENGYUAN 8: 201 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-6a.1">令尹曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-6a.2">“甚善.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-6a.3">安樹【10】坐友三人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0076_tls_001-6a.4">立友三人.【11正】</seg></p>

